        java.util.List<GroupFilter> search(GroupFilterQuery query)
                                   throws DaoException
        Searches group filters according to the given query, ordering by name. If no group filter can be found, returns an empty List. If any exception is thrown by the underlying implementation, it should be wrapped by a DaoException.
